seulement leur intitul\u00e9.</Description><Description language-id="de_DE">Ergebnisse nur mit ihrem Titel anzeigen.</Description><Description language-id="hu_HU">Az eredm\u00e9nyeket csak a c\u00edm\u00fckkel jelen\u00edtse meg.</Description><Description language-id="ja_JP">\u7d50\u679c\u306b\u3064\u3044\u3066\u30bf\u30a4\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u307f\u3092\u8868\u793a\u3057\u307e\u3059\u3002</Description><Description language-id="pt_BR">Exibir resultados com apenas seus t\u00edtulos.</Description><Description language-id="es_ES">Muestra resultados solo con el t\u00edtulo.</Description><Description language-id="sv_SE">Visa bara resultat med titel.</Description><Description language-id="zh_TW">\u50c5\u4ee5\u6a19\u984c\u986f\u793a\u7d50\u679c\u3002</Description></root>','ftl','<div class="c-mb-4 c-mt-4 search-total-label">\u000a\u0009<#if searchContainer.getTotal() == 1>\u000a\u0009\u0009${languageUtil.format(locale, "x-result-for-x", [searchContainer.getTotal(), "<strong>" + htmlUtil.escape(searchResultsPortletDisplayContext.getKeywords()) + "</strong>"], false)}\u000a\u0009<#else>\u000a\u0009\u0009${languageUtil.format(locale, "x-results-for-x", [searchContainer.getTotal(), "<strong>" + htmlUtil.escape(searchResultsPortletDisplayContext.getKeywords()) + "</strong>"], false)}\u000a\u0009</#if>\u000a</div>\u000a\u000a<div class="display-compact">\u000a\u0009<ul class="list-unstyled">\u000a\u0009\u0009<#if entries?has_content>\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009<#list entries as entry>\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009<li class="align-items-center d-flex">\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009<div class="c-mb-2 c-mt-2">\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009<a class="link-primary single-link" href="${entry.getViewURL()}">\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009${entry.getHighlightedTitle()}\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009</a>\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009</div>\u000a\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009\u0009<#if entry.isAssetRendererURLDownloadVisible()>\u000a\u0009\u000